        "product_description": {
            "value": "GEAR AID Tenacious Tape is an ultra-strong, peel-and-stick repair and seam tape designed to fix rips and holes fast without heat or sewing. Ideal for tents, tarps, jackets, vinyl furniture, and other outdoor gear, this durable tape features an aggressive adhesive that bonds permanently to nylon, mesh, vinyl, rubber, and plastic. Its waterproof coating creates a washable repair that won't peel off over time, ensuring long-lasting protection for your equipment. The clear vinyl finish delivers nearly invisible repairs, keeping your gear looking great while extending its life. This roll measures 1.5 inches by 60 inches, providing plenty of tape for multiple repairs. Not recommended for use on seams, denim, cotton, or natural fabrics. Whether you're patching a leaking tent, mending a torn jacket, or repairing worn vinyl furniture, Tenacious Tape offers a fast, reliable, and mess-free solution. Packaging may vary.",
